JavaAssignment.Model

Class Matrix

  • java.lang.Object
    • JavaAssignment.Model.Matrix

  • public class Matrix
extends java.lang.Object
    Matrix is based on 2 dimensional ArrayList of Doubles. Matrix class allows to crate matrix based on ArrayList of ArrayList.
